  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  OnSelectSFX: {fileID: 0}
  skillType: 0
  skillName: 45
  skillNameText: A nice-looking piece of rock
  skillDescription: Gains a 5.2% buff in <color=green>HP</color>, <color=#ff4545>ATK</color>,
    <color=#00ffe1>MSPD</color> and <color=#ffd61f>ASPD</color>. Special and skill
    cooldowns -5.2%. The first time HP reaches 0, immediately <color=green>restores
    52% max HP</color> and gains 1.52 seconds of invulnerability.
  favorText: Even if it is an unassuming piece of ore that is covered in dirt, if
    she gives you a present, please accept it. It must be something she likes a lot
    and wants to share with you anyway.
  skillDescriptionInShort: Gains a 5.2% buff in atrributes and CDs. The first time
    HP reaches 0, immediately <color=green>restores 52% max HP</color> and gains
    1.52 seconds of invulnerability.
