  skillType: 1
  skillName: 16
  skillNameText: Zeropoint Burst - Snow Blossom
  skillDescription: '''Zeropoint Burst''''s minimum freeze duration increases by
    1 second. Enemies hit by this skill creates an extra ''Zeropoint Burst'' around
    them, whose maximum freeze duration equals to the current freeze duration of
    the enemy starting it. Can only trigger once per enemy.'
  favorText: '"Please calm down a little!"'
  skillDescriptionInShort: '''Zeropoint Burst'' now spreads the freeze to nearby
    enemies around the targets.'
  mutuallyExclusiveSkills: 1100000012000000
  Overlay: {fileID: 0}
