  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  OnSelectSFX: {fileID: 0}
  skillType: 1
  skillName: 52
  skillNameText: '''Anthem of the Wind'''
  skillDescription: 'For melee player: Every attack land shortens the cool-down of
    ''Evasion'' by 0.75 seconds, every ''Evasion'' usage shortens the cool-down of
    ''Juggernaut'' by 4 seconds, every ''Juggernaut'' usage grants +12 ASPD, lasts
    15 seconds and stacks up to 6 times. At max stacks, gains an additional +36%
    MSPD and all effects are doubled.'
  favorText: Her book alone can only carry words, her arts unit alone is just a staff,
    her originium arts alone does not excel. But, combined them together, with a
    little more work, and even the wind will bow to her.
  skillDescriptionInShort: 
  mutuallyExclusiveSkills: 
  Overlay: {fileID: 0}
