      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "<size=20><b><color=#ff00ff>Cautious Level:</b></color></size> \n\nA distance
    measured by a percentage of the unit's attack range.\n\n- Melee enemy only attacks
    if the player is within this distance. Higher cautious level means shorter distance.\n\n-
    Ranged unit runs away from the player if they are within this distance. HIgher
    cautious level means higher distance."
