  skillType: 1
  skillName: 51
  skillNameText: Der Tag Neight Sich - Widely Read
  skillDescription: Cancelling 'Der Tag Neight Sich' refunds a portion of its cool-down
    based on the remaining duration, up to 80% within the first 0.5 seconds.
  favorText: She is distractable, but this isn't to say she has no sense of priority.
    When a directly pressing matter is at hand, she focuses and spares no detail
    until it's done, but the moment the most critical part is finished, she loosens
    up, and it's then that something else can easily steal her attention.
  skillDescriptionInShort: Cancelling 'Der Tag Neight Sich' refunds a portion of
    its cool-down based on the remaining duration.
  mutuallyExclusiveSkills: 1b0000001c000000270000001d000000
  Overlay: {fileID: 0}
